Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Statement and Disclosure describes the types of information Anova collects when you visit our website, use our mobile applications or Wi-Fi-connected appliances, or otherwise interact with us. This Privacy Statement also explains how Anova may use and disclose such information, and your ability to control certain uses of it.
